# Backend API base URL used by the frontend (axios). BAKED IN AT BUILD TIME.
#
#   "/api/v1"  (recommended)  → relative; the dev/preview server proxies it to the
#                               backend. Works for ALL users in dev AND production.
#
#   "http://HOST:PORT/api/v1" → absolute; ONLY if the backend is reachable at that
#                               exact URL FROM THE USER'S BROWSER.
#                               ⚠ Never use "localhost" for a deployed server — to a
#                               remote visitor, localhost is THEIR machine, not yours.
VITE_API_URL=/api/v1
